Docs.param:
Scope for the token acquisition.  By default this is api://AzureAdTokenExchange/.default.
            for other clouds, you would need to override it:

api://AzureAdTokenExchange/.defaultfor public cloudapi://AzureADTokenExchangeChina/.defaultfor China cloudapi://AzureADTokenExchangeFrance/.defaultfor Bleuapi://AzureADTokenExchangeGermany/.defaultfor the German cloud
